Program: The Why Factor
Title: Why Eye Contact is Important
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p020gkp8
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 16 Jun 2014
Why is making eye contact so important? Catching someone’s eyes across a crowded room can lead to a passionate love affair. Yet catching the wrong person’s eye in a bar could lead to a tussle of another kind. Mikes Williams explores why eye contact is an essential part of a baby’s development; how it is used to attract a partner and what our eyes give away about us, which is beyond our control. (Photo: Eyes making contact. Credit: Shutterstock) Show less